snippet: Park won in Taiwan for her third victory of the year and 12th career title, holding off Stacy Lewis by two strokes at Miramar in Taipei.
abstract: Inbee Park wins LPGA Taiwan Championship for her third victory of 2014 and 12th career title; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Park won in Taiwan for her third victory of the year and 12th career title, holding off Stacy Lewis by two strokes at Miramar in Taipei.

headline.main: Inbee Park Hangs On to Win L.P.G.A. Taiwan Championship
headline.print_headline: Park Hangs on to Win in Taiwan
